name: Glimmergiggle, the Gelatinous SpriteFlamingo
text: In the Twilight Marsh, Glimmergiggle flitted, her laughter tinkling like crystal chimes. Translucent wings shimmered, casting prism-dances on awed lilies. Creatures peered from water’s edge, spellbound. When moon rose, her giggles softened, echoes of joy in the hush. Marsh slept, dreaming in Glimmergiggle’s radiant, jelly-hued hues.
